#18153
#RBaal's Piece of Hell~
#0The floor is covered in a thick, black, blood-like liquid.  You hear what 
seems to be a very sinister and loud laughter coming  from the shadows 
but you can't make out if anyone is sitting there or if you’re starting to go 
mad.  As you turn to go back the way you came you notice that the black 
liquid that was once the floor has now formed an exit in every direction.  
The ground trembles under your feet and feel a hot breath on the back of 
your neck.  You spin around and see nothing, only blackness.
If one were to fly above, perhaps one should look for somethinginteresting?
~
